title: The expected delivery date in Australia for Google Pixel 5 preorder through Google Store?
content: I did a a preorder for Google Pixel 5 on 1st October through Google store to deliver it to my Australian address. It's mentioned in the order details as to be delivered by "November 5-6". But, I see now with the preorder options shows up with Vodafone and Optus websites, the delivery-date as "October-15". So, which one is correct? Any idea?
